{"tid":822604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面對日本人口老化　安倍晉三製造不退休社會","createTime":"2018-09-16T11:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T20:09:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"018d693a61f57fe6ddf34f9f4e269141091d6c43","tid":822604,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180914/photo/bkn-20180914102447384-0914_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180914113527\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180914%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180914102447384-0914_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180914113527&h=c3d35030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外電報道，日本首相安倍晉三揚言，計劃用接下來的1年時間，製造不論多大年紀、只要有意願就能參加工作的「終身不退休」、「終身活躍」的社會。<br />\n<br />\n他補充，政府將製造允許65歲以上人士繼續工作的體制，有必要極大提升職業中期人員就業；另外，不排除將養老金領取門檻上調至70歲以上。<br />\n<br />\n他透露，計劃利用接下來的兩年時間，以「終身不退休、終身活躍」為前提，期望通過3年時間，推進醫療和養老金等社會保障大規模改革，構建所有年齡層都能安心的社會保障制度。<br />\n<br />\n此前，日本應對人口老化問題的奇招還包括對工業機器人的應用。據國際機器人協會(IFR)數據，2016年全球工業機器人密度排名中，日本高居全球第4，每萬名員工中擁有303部工業機器人，僅次於南韓、新加坡及德國。"},{"pid":"7357d92d39e5534c1ad2787b42ff4d6bcaac8617","tid":822604,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180914/mobile/bkn-20180914102447384-0914_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180914%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180914102447384-0914_00842_001.html&d=2HZR13ScHSfrg7ZxgP%2BkhV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=35421906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180914/mobile/bkn-20180914102447384-0914_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6beefb45b11d853b24242c2a6d5c67cb71a7109d","tid":822604,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbe49ea77a67259a00a23161c89d4e951468216","tid":822604,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207eed2dac69c88aed5379aac29baa53d647b526","tid":822604,"uid":9736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"老屎忽長存"},{"pid":"4219d37782cb606882e6cf2366f5b18c58153fa2","tid":822604,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T19:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7761f3af0c38e900bd2a75ae28f295ae2f47b8c","tid":822604,"uid":2674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"207eed2dac69c88aed5379aac29baa53d647b526","tid":822604,"uid":9736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"老屎忽長存"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T20:09:19.000Z","msg":"唔係，佢諗法係想迫撚死d老人家，等政府唔洗俾返d強姦金佢，解決赤字"}]}